column1: #Text=Hold a Dog and Tickle Its Toes
#Text=When owning a pupper and having the urge to tickle it , you want to do it properly so that your doggo does n't give you strange looks or misunderstand your intentions .
#Text=If your doge is n't ready for this kind of intimacy you might consider talking about it with them or waiting until your relationship is ready for it .
#Text=To do the Lappy Tappy , you must first get the doggo into your lap .
#Text=If your dog is smaller this step is easier to do because you can usually just pick it up .
#Text=However , If your dog is bigger you might have to lure your dog .
#Text=Here are some ways to get the dog into position :
#Text=Treats ! Find treats that your dog enjoys and tempt them by teasing or leaving a trail to your lap .
#Text=Your dog probably loves you , but if they do n't you might try just using a tone of voice that is non-threatening and saying something like , " Here puppy .
